column10:
The assistant was useful for finding information that I did not have. The help came mostly with simple factual inquiries (e.g., year of authorship, define list of food commodities, water content of fat, water content of muscle). 

The assistant was less helpful in certain cases of trivial questions that I would have expected to come easy. For example, I was able to retrieve the number of internet users of India in 2017 and I was able to retrieve the total population of India in 2017. The question responses needed a percentage, and I felt there were two responses  that were within range  from my estimation, but neither seemed correct. I was unable to get an answer for a simple arithmetic inquiry (402/1324). Now that I am reflecting, I wonder if I would have had greater success with replacing the punctuation with the worded long form, 402 divided by 1324.
